      "part_type": "Hadith",
      "path": "/books/kitab-al-zuhd:2:17:6",
      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/31/2/17/6",
      "text": [
        ": سمعت أبا عبد الله عليه السلام يقول: إن المؤمن يعطى يوم القيامة كتابا منشورا (كتاب منشور) مكتوب فيه: كتاب الله العزيز الحكيم ادخلوا فلانا الجنة."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.shaykh-tahir-ridha-jaffer": [
          "6.Al-Qāsim narrated from ʿAlī, from Abū Baṣīr who said, “I heard Abā ʿAbdillāh (a) say, ‘Verily the believer will be given, on the Day of Judgment, an opened scroll in which will be written: “[This is] a decree of Allah, the Mighty, the Wise. Admit so-and-so into Paradise.”’”"
        ]
      }
    },
